<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" data-pin-description="These pink cupcakes are light and fluffy pink velvet cake topped with a swirl of homemade cream cheese frosting and sprinkles. An easy and delicious dessert that's perfect for parties!" data-pin-title="Pink Cupcakes" src="https://www.dinneratthezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/pink-cupcakes-final-2.jpg" alt="A pink cupcake cut in half." class="wp-image-48113" srcset="https://www.dinneratthezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/pink-cupcakes-final-2.jpg 1200w, https://www.dinneratthezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/pink-cupcakes-final-2-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://www.dinneratthezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/pink-cupcakes-final-2-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.dinneratthezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/pink-cupcakes-final-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.dinneratthezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/pink-cupcakes-final-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.dinneratthezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/pink-cupcakes-final-2-276x414.jpg 276w, https://www.dinneratthezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/pink-cupcakes-final-2-128x192.jpg 128w, https://www.dinneratthezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/pink-cupcakes-final-2-378x567.jpg 378w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" data-pin-media="https://www.dinneratthezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/pink-cupcakes-final-2.jpg"></figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-flavor-variations">Flavor Variations</h2>



<p>These cupcakes are perfect as-is, but you can easily customize them to suit your tastes.</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Color: Not in a pink kind of mood? You can literally use any color of food coloring to transform these pink velvet cupcakes into red velvet cupcakes, purple cupcakes, green cupcakes or any other shade of the rainbow!</li>



<li>Add-Ins: You can stir up to 1/2 cup of pink jimmy sprinkles or white chocolate chips into your cake batter.</li>



<li>Toppings: Feel free to add different toppings to your cupcakes aside from sprinkles. Some great options include pastel colored M&amp;M&rsquo;s, a drizzle of white chocolate, pink sanding sugar or fresh raspberries.</li>
</ul>



<p>Pink cupcakes are always a huge hit, no matter what occasion you happen to be celebrating!</p>


