<div class="cwp-food-content">
	<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">These pink cupcakes are light and fluffy pink velvet cake topped with a swirl of homemade cream cheese frosting and sprinkles. An easy and delicious dessert that's perfect for parties!</span></div>
